I just played a game (ranked flex) and i was adc as Vayne and my support was Thresh as the game went on we absolutely stomped the enemy bot-lane. Now i ended up the game 21/4/10 and i got S- im not complaining but considering that my support finished the game 1/0/31 and got a S- it&acute;s pretty hilarious xD.
So i think Riot should do something to improve the grading system but it&acute;s nothing that im totally mad at i actually think it was pretty funny.

